title: #152: Sam and XG Answer Your Questions On The Happy New Year
description: Thank you for tuning in for another fun festive episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This end of year podcast episode XG and myself answer all of your questions.  Thank you so much for all of your love and support.  We couldn't have done it without you.  Happy New Year to all you Ronin, Mad Hatters and all of you Truth Seekers! 2019 is going to be insane!
